  • Detailer and Lot Manager at Luther Burnsville Hyundai (6 mo.)

  • Detailer at Valley Buick GMC (current, 1 yr.)

I have worked two jobs as well that were not at car dealerships, those are:

    • I mounted and balanced tires.

  • Peer Tutor at DCTC (current, 1 mo.)

    • I assist students with any help they need, specificly IT classes, such as Intro to Java.
